### Get all technicians
GET http://localhost:8080/technicians

### Search technicians by expertise (example: electrician)
GET http://localhost:8080/search/electrician

### Search technicians by name (example: John)
GET http://localhost:8080/search?name=John

### Search technicians by ID (example: 1)
GET http://localhost:8080/search?id=1

### Book appointment for technician with ID 1
POST http://localhost:8080/1/book
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appointmentDate": "05/05/2025",
  "customerName": "Alice"
}

### Book appointment with missing fields (should fail)
POST http://localhost:8080/2/book
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appointmentDate": "01/05/2025"
}

### Try booking again for same technician (should return error)
POST http://localhost:8080/1/book
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appointmentDate": "03/05/2025",
  "customerName": "Bob"
}
